      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lean beef meatballs with creamy linguine</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining chopped dill</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
